{"tid":1450541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警狗還眼」明日1PM 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:02:01.000Z","uid":2559,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f37ba1d2b6c881d73d6160bc41430a14254d20b6","tid":1450541,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"c0fbc430bbcc0adab0109cb4240319ee8e0eb75f","tid":1450541,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"493072c70ae1bf9ed3ad04246464b86343615c22","tid":1450541,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e03b07ce79f00988d9ac970d9996c704551eb61","tid":1450541,"uid":228175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"856736d56ee456ec775de80b5963bbabdee2acd0","tid":1450541,"uid":99946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb47f81693eefd5bb74c15c4cfb00851aa08cdf4","tid":1450541,"uid":103105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zt51x76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZt51x76.jpg&h=53cd5489&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d261395eb22ebf80ac5a6e64b3959221847459b5","tid":1450541,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:02:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}